cloudworkstation (0.4.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Phase 4 Complete: Enterprise Research Management Platform
    - Project-based organization with role-based access control
    - Advanced budget management with real-time tracking and alerts
    - Cost analytics with detailed hibernation savings analysis
    - Multi-user collaboration with granular permissions (Owner/Admin/Member/Viewer)
    - Enterprise API for project management and budget monitoring
    - Budget automation with configurable alerts and automated actions
  * Template System Enhancements
    - Complete template inheritance system with validation
    - Template stacking and composition support
    - Comprehensive validation suite with clear error messages
  * Hibernation Ecosystem Complete
    - Manual hibernation controls with intelligent fallback
    - Automated hibernation policies with configurable thresholds
    - Domain-specific hibernation optimization
    - Complete audit trail of cost-saving actions
  * Multi-Modal Access Achievement
    - Cross-platform GUI with system tray integration
    - Enhanced TUI interface with professional styling
    - Feature parity across CLI, TUI, and GUI interfaces
    - Unified daemon architecture with REST API
  * Security and Compliance
    - Enhanced security hardening with comprehensive audit logging
    - NIST 800-171 compliance framework implementation
    - Advanced keychain integration and tamper detection
    - Secure profile management with encryption

