cloudworkstation (0.4.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major Release: Multi-Modal Access Implementation
    - New cross-platform GUI interface with Fyne framework
    - Enhanced TUI interface with BubbleTea framework
    - Unified daemon architecture providing REST API
    - Complete feature parity across CLI, TUI, and GUI
  * Advanced Hibernation System
    - Intelligent hibernation with automatic fallback to stop
    - Cost optimization through session-preserving hibernation
    - Automated hibernation policies for hands-off operation
  * Template Application Engine
    - Dynamic template application to running instances
    - Incremental updates with rollback support
    - Template difference analysis and preview
  * Profile System Integration
    - Seamless AWS credential and region management
    - Profile switching across all interfaces
    - Enhanced security with keychain integration

